{"tid":20904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］巨乳媽媽的士餵奶 司機忍不住偷拍","createTime":"2016-12-03T14:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T10:37:40.000Z","uid":5995,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aefb1b967a4191b796118aa9ab7e221d0c2b33f1","tid":20904,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:41:28.000Z","msg":"一名的士司機上載乘客餵哺母乳的相片facebook，惹起網民強烈反感，不少人認為是對偉大母愛的一種侮辱。今早《蘋果》接獲多名讀者反映，指有的士司機涉嫌將一名婦人在車廂內餵哺母乳的相片公諸網上，原相更加未有打格，認為該司機變態及可恥，更批評司機「人渣、賤格」。據了解，相片是由一名自稱是的士司機的姓周網民於今日清晨約5時許上傳至facebook群組，照片可見在的士車廂內，乘客位一名婦人將圓領衣衫拉低，露出半邊胸，為嬰兒餵哺母乳。姓周網民同時留言指：「咁都得？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/224019_10c964199d11fb5fb35c8e9814ee649f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F224019_10c964199d11fb5fb35c8e9814ee649f.jpg&h=6e7ee683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161203&amp;guid=55998475&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161203%26guid%3D55998475%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8AT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=965ebfd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161203%26guid%3D55998475%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=e15cbd00\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161203&amp;guid=55998475&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"df0c0fcc28880a9414458c748a6bfae6d9c952e6","tid":20904,"uid":23221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:39:31.000Z","msg":"純文字討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8b90668c2f44844fbc0055044dc4b71daac268","tid":20904,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dis